  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to measure the ability of balance controlling and test the
      evaluation of clinical trials with different arch insoles. The investigators want to find out
      the difference and efficacy of arch insoles in the dynamic postural control for the elderly.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
